booth.description:
If you need to ship packages to your stand, Bella Center uses the freight company DSV for storage, handling and delivery to stand in Expo.

Ordering will happen through our sponsor configurator portal, where you can choose pre-event/post-event handling, storage, customs clearance, etc.

1) Log in to the sponsor configurator portal: {{configuratorUrl}}
2) Go to the shop, filter on 'Package Handling' and select the needed services, then add it to your cart. You can adjust the quantity if needed.
3) Select 'Proceed to Checkout' to confirm the order.
4) You can either save the contract as a PDF and sign it using your preferred method, or scroll down and digitally sign directly in the configurator.

Note: Payments are not handled through the portal. We will arrange payment with you separately.
----------------------------
Please ship the items to the address below with clear markings:

{{editionCode}} / <StandNumber as informed by {{leadContactName}}> / {{companyName}}
{{shippingAddressDsv}}
Mark: 1 of ... / 2 of ... / 3 of ... etc.

Questions to ordering can be directed to {{leadContactName}} - {{leadContactEmail}}

Questions to freight company, DSV Fairs & Events:
Tel: {{freightContactPhone}}
Email: {{freightContactEmail}}

For Shipments outside the EU we require the following documents for customs clearance:
* 3 originals of proforma invoice / packing list in English, showing weights, sizes, values, description of content and Harmonized Codes
* Separate invoices for temporary goods (Exhibits / Standfittings) and final importation (consumables / advertising materials) or send temporary goods by ATA Carnet
* If necessary: Certificate of Origin (Form A / EUR.1) / Special certificates (Health / veterinary)
